    </h1>
    <article data-scroll-group data-scroll-step="110">
      <p>My research asks how representations are formed, changed, used, and controlled across minds and machines. I am interested in how experience becomes structure, how that structure supports memory, reasoning, generalization, and action, and why it sometimes becomes unstable, misleading, or difficult to control.</p>
      <transition name="research-details">
